		<td colspan="2">Firstly, you need to check the guild rules listed on the site, to ensure that you are happy with all here, and willing to abide by them without exception.<br>Then- E mail to salem@btclick.com<br>Your title line should read-<br>GUILD APPLICATION CLASS/LEVEL/RACE/TIME ZONE i.e. UK(GMT/BST) or US (EST/PST/CST*)<br>*-whichever appropriate.<br><br>You should then list the following with the letter prefix in your mail.<br><br>A- Your age group - 1) 16-18  2) 19-23  3) 24-32 4) 33+<br>B- Your 3 main likes and dislikes about EQ<br>C- Your approximate average playtime on a daily/weekly basis, and which times between on your timezone.<br>D- A short note, in 30 words or less, why you would like to join our guild.<br><br>We will endeavour to answer all applications within 72 hours. If successful you will be guilded for one calendar months' trial. If for some reason at the end of this period you are unsucessful, you will be given a full reason and chance for discussion with the Guildleader or an appointed officer.<br><br>Good luck!<br><br>Guildleader Admin.</td>
